 {"id":"bd-yx9r.7.2","title":"Port service-builder and transport-layer stacks","description":"The upstream crate provides a service stack (, , , , , , , , , , etc.) and transport adapters (, , , , mocks). ANSI C has almost none of this layer.","design":"Port these as reusable public modules with clear buffering/backpressure/failure semantics and deterministic logging hooks.","acceptance_criteria":"A. Service and transport public APIs cover the core upstream layers.\\nB. Tests cover buffering, retry/timeout/load-shed behavior, routing, aggregation, and reconnect/error paths.\\nC. At least one integration lane exercises a service stack over a transport with structured logs.","notes":"This is a key dependency for HTTP, gRPC, messaging, and database client work.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:30.102564073Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:07.952354189Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["crate-parity","service","transport"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.7.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:06.180359106Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.7.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:07.067137591Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.7.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:07.951631992Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.7.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.7","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:30.102564073Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.7.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.7.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:34.920352651Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.7.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.8.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"20