 {"id":"bd-yx9r.7.3","title":"Port remote, migration, conformance, and spork/operator orchestration surfaces","description":"The Rust crate exposes remote/migration/spork/conformance-oriented surfaces that turn the runtime into an operable system rather than only an execution engine. ANSI C needs comparable operator/developer entry points or explicit, well-tested exclusions.","design":"Implement the public orchestration helpers and conformance-facing entry points needed to drive cross-runtime scenarios, migrations, and operator workflows.","acceptance_criteria":"A. Public APIs exist for the relevant orchestration surfaces or explicit fail-closed exclusions are encoded.\\nB. Integration tests cover representative workflows and operator-visible diagnostics.\\nC. Artifact/reporting formats align with A3's expanded verification contract.","notes":"Should share evidence/logging machinery with C3 and D2 rather than inventing new report formats.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:31.330072451Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:48.555193762Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["conformance","crate-parity","remote","spork"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.7.3","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:08.828826742Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.7.3","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:09.733567644Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.7.3","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:10.621720607Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.7.3","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.7","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:31.330072451Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.7.3","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.7.1","type":"blo